{"tid":519260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大律師公會主席：法治無客觀標準　指「法治已死」是誇張失實","createTime":"2018-01-04T07:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T13:25:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7df266bf65a9faae3e903417ce51666e8f39c468","tid":519260,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T07:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180104/s00001/77b786c50cc620cbb6b5529faf31008d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180104%2Fs00001%2F77b786c50cc620cbb6b5529faf31008d.jpg&h=7570bfaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180104/s00001/1515035620900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180104%2Fs00001%2F1515035620900&d=YksBNBJox1AExyUYcoq%2Fdr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f8e69fb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180104%2Fs00001%2F1515035620900&h=9131507c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180104/s00001/1515035620900</a><br />\n<br />\n連日接受多家傳媒訪問的大律師公會主席林定國，於商台訪問中指出，「法治」是「一國兩制」中最容易引起摩擦的地方，「法治」沒有客觀量度標準，很視乎市民信心，而雖然「法治」偶有受到衝擊，惟表現已相當不錯，認為「法治已死」的說法是誇張失實，香港不應妄自菲薄。<br />\n<br />\n林定國表示，他與內地司法人員交流中，感到中央愈來愈重視法律工作，希望中央能從香港體會到「法治」對維持社會穩定，以及令人感到公平正義的重要。他又期望中央理解普通法概念，於處理涉及香港事務問題上多交流溝通。"},{"pid":"a5d8e040be1a7f14c9918038b8613d447631f61f","tid":519260,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T07:31:56.000Z","msg":"大既律師喎  <br />\n<br />\n笑撚死人<br />\n<br />\nLLB YEAR 1 無讀 rule of law？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid